&lt;p&gt;We are seeking Nurses with Emergency Department experience and expertise to join our team. We are currently building our team and are seeking competent nurses who have the desire to develop and build a team with us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to have the skills and abilities to deliver high standards of care and have the resilience to meet the challenges of our busy and stimulating work environment. You should be self-motivated, an excellent communicator and have proven organisational and clinical skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information and an informal meeting to discuss opportunities contact:&lt;/p&gt;
